text: The 1969 World Table Tennis Championships – Women's Singles was the 30th edition of the women's singles championship. Toshiko Kowada defeated Gabriele Geissler in the final by three sets to one, to win the title. ==Results== ==See also== List of World Table Tennis Championships medalists ==References== \- Category:1969 in women's table tennis Table
